title: Ron Funches
itunes:title: Ron Funches
description:
Comedian Ron Funches is back!  But first, Whitney catches everyone up on her trip and new epiphanies on the Illuminati.  Then Ron talks about making Will Ferrell laugh and how to know when you've won.  Ron's new show LOOT is streaming now on Apple TV+ and to see him on tour go to https://ronfunches.com/  His podcast GETTIN BETTER is available wherever you get your pods.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
